# Note: ZEPTO_TOKEN is required as a Supabase Edge Function secret, not a local environment variable
# Set this in your Supabase project dashboard under Edge Functions > send-email > Environment Variables

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Residential-rental monetization (Phase A–G).
# These are Edge Function SECRETS, not VITE_ vars. Set them in:
#   Supabase dashboard → Project Settings → Edge Functions → Secrets
# (or via: supabase secrets set KEY=value)
#
# Stripe API
#   STRIPE_API_KEY              # already used by existing functions
#   STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET       # already used by existing functions
#
# Listing subscriptions (Agent / VIP) and Concierge add-on price IDs.
# Create three recurring monthly prices in Stripe and paste the IDs here:
#   STRIPE_AGENT_PRICE_ID            # $50 / month
#   STRIPE_VIP_PRICE_ID              # $100 / month
#   STRIPE_ADDON_CONCIERGE_PRICE_ID  # $50 / month (only chargeable bundled with Agent/VIP)
#
# NOTE — Individual listing payments ($25 first month, $15 renewal, multi-month
# packages) do NOT need pre-created Stripe Price objects. The checkout uses
# ad-hoc `price_data` and reads dollar amounts from
#   src/types/monetization.ts → INDIVIDUAL_LISTING_PACKAGES
#   supabase/functions/_shared/stripe-prices.ts → INDIVIDUAL_LISTING_PACKAGES
# (the two are kept in sync manually). To change pricing, edit those two files.
#
# Twilio (already used by existing SMS flows; reused by send-paid-listing-reminders).
#   TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID
#   TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN
#   TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER
#
# Public site URL (used in SMS body checkout links).
#   PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://hadirot.com
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
